************************

 The _XSLT-process_ mode is part of XEmacs, but it works with both
XEmacs and GNU Emacs. The installation differs slighly between the two
editors as we will see shortly.  The mode has been tested on Linux
and Windows 2000, with XEmacs and GNU Emacs, and under MacOS X with
GNU Emacs (http://webweavertech.com/ovidiu/emacs.html). The
development platform however is Linux, so expect this to be the most
stable one. 

